{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}

{% block title %}About - Sanity Shop{% endblock %}

{% block body %}
    <style>
        body {
            background: #222;
            text-align: center;
        }
        header h1 {
            color: #ff6600;
            font-size: 3em;
            text-shadow: 3px 3px 5px #ff6600;
        }
        h2 {
            color: #ff6600;
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 3px #ff6600;
        }
        .banner {
            width: 100%;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 5px solid #ff6600;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            line-height: 1.6;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
            color: #000000;
        }
        p b {
            color: #ff6600;
        }
        .disclaimer {
            background: #333;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            border: 1px dashed #ff6600;
            margin-top: 20px;
            color: #ffcc00;
        }
        .ghostly-text {
            font-style: italic;
            color: #ff6600;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 5px #ffcc00;
        }
        .highlight {
            color: #ffcc00;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
    <body>
    <header>
        <h1>Sanity Shop - Where the Dead Shop!</h1>
    </header>
    <main>
        <img src="{{ asset('images/logo.png') }}" alt="Sanity Shop logo" class="banner">
        <h2>About Us - Your One Stop for Ghostly Goods</h2>
        <p>Welcome to <span class="highlight">Sanity Shop</span>, where we bring the “boo” to your budget! Got a haunted house with ghosts that won’t pay rent? We’ve got just the thing for that.</p>
        <p>Our shelves are stocked with <span class="ghostly-text">ghost-repellent sprays</span>, <span class="ghostly-text">banshee earplugs</span>, and the latest in <span class="ghostly-text">specter-chasing technology</span>. Trying to chat with a poltergeist? Check out our deluxe Ouija boards—now with typo-correcting planchettes!</p>
        <p>Headed to a graveyard at midnight? Don’t forget our <span class="ghostly-text">glow-in-the-dark salt circles</span> and <span class="ghostly-text">anti-possession thermal blankets</span>. They’re a must-have for anyone dealing with cranky spirits.</p>
        <p>We believe every ghost hunter deserves quality gear—because nothing ruins a good haunting like being unprepared. </p>
        <p>So gear up, stay sane, and remember: the dead don’t rest, but at least you can—with our haunted-approved sleep masks!</p>
        <div class="disclaimer">
            <b>Disclaimer:</b> They don't block the noise... but they’ll block your nightmares.
        </div>
    </main>
    </body>
{% endblock %}
